---
title: Sticky Asian Veggie Mince & Garlic Rice with Veggie Stir-Fry & Crushed Peanuts
description: A stir-fry sauce can do no wrong, in fact it’s perfection when cooked with veggie mince, creating lovely sticky flavours. There’s
veggies and a fragrant garlic rice to absorb all the leftover sauce. It’s too good to miss!

